divs: Sighting DetailsI am driving west on hwy.71 about halfway between Bastrop and Austin. I notice a dark object in the sky approaching towards me at a low altitude. I see that is has no wings,no engine, I hear no sound. It looks a little like the front end of an F-117. It has some kind of flap on the rearend. I see the flap rise up and the aircraft does the same, going up above and out of sight. I look around but see nothing. I have never seen anything like this, and think that it is a ufo. It really moved like nothing I know of can. There were a few other cars on the road, but this happened in such a short amount of time that no one else may have seen it.
Summary: saw what I think was a ufo
trends: There have been 188 other sightings in Austin
